    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="计算机科学导论"><a href="#计算机科学导论" class="headerlink" title="计算机科学导论"></a>计算机科学导论</h2><h2 id="hexadecimal"><a href="#hexadecimal" class="headerlink" title="hexadecimal"></a>hexadecimal</h2><hr><p>Why do we need hexadecimal?</p><p>1.A compact way of write down very large numbers.</p><p>2.Used for colour codes, memory address, encryption keys······</p><p>3.easy to convert to and from binary.</p><blockquote><p>compact 紧凑的</p><p>encryption 加密</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    
